        "Nowadays, a large number of children allocate their time to using cell phones. In my opinion, it's totally a negative phenomenon and I'll explain my reasons in the forthcoming paragraphs.",
        "because of the technological advancements that have been made in recent decades, society is forcing everyone to use their smartphones anywhere at any time. For instance, lots of teachers nowadays, give assignments to their students via",
